      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated with exacting standards, remaining in a state of preservation that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless mechanical synchronization, confirms its status as a premier example of the marque. We invite the most discerning clientele to acquire this benchmark of automotive excellence.",
